  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Quiz Magic Academy DS - Two Space-Time Stones - is the second QMA consumer game. The genre of the quiz and the flow of the lessons are based on the arcade version 6, and the background and music of 6 are also used.\nElements added in 5 and later, such as the final cut-in, certification exam and touch panel quiz, are also implemented.\nCharacter information is based on 6.\nThe character's graphics are from 4 and earlier, with some changes.",
